snippet.title: Johnny Depp Accuses Amber Heard Of Faking Bruises To Fabricate Domestic Abuse Claims
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp continued to deny Amber Heard's abuse allegations in new court documents from his $50 million defamation lawsuit against his ex-wife. Watch for the latest on their contentious legal battle.
